schemas.name: all.types.graphql
schemas.content:
type Query{
    #get all kinds of file and it's url in specified bucket
    all(bucketName:String):AllData
}

#file info
type File{
    id:Int
    rawName:String
    name:String
    tags:[String]
    type:String
    size:Int
    contentSecret:String
    createDate:String
    updateDate:String
    url:String
}

#image info
type Image{
    id:Int
    rawName:String
    name:String
    tags:[String]
    type:String
    size:Int
    createDate:String
    updateDate:String
    width:Int
    height:Int
    url:String
}

#audio info
type Audio{
    id:Int
    rawName:String
    name:String
    tags:[String]
    md5:String
    type:String
    size:Int
    createDate:String
    updateDate:String
    url:String
}

#video info
type Video{
    id:Int
    rawName:String
    name:String
    tags:[String]
    type:String
    size:Int
    createDate:String
    updateDate:String
    url:String
}

#document info
type Document{
    id:Int
    rawName:String
    name:String
    tags:[String]
    type:String
    size:Int
    createDate:String
    updateDate:String
    url:String
}

#return data
type AllData{
    #error data
    code:Int
    #error message
    message:String
    #base url for visit file , need to append the url of info
    baseUrl:String
    #array of file info 
    files:[File]
    #array of image info 
    images:[Image]
    #array of audio info
    audios:[Audio]
    #array of video info
    videos:[Video]
    #array of document info
    documents:[Document]
}

schemas.name: buckets.types.graphql
schemas.content:
type Query{
    #get information of bucket,return id、publicOrPrivate、name
    buckets:BucketsData
}

#information of bucket
type Bucket{
    #id
    id:Int
    #public bucket or private bucket
    publicOrPrivate:String
    #bucket name
    name:String
}

#return data
type BucketsData{
    #error code
    code:Int
    #error message
    message:String
    #array of bucket information
    buckets:[Bucket]
}

schemas.name: downloadProcess.types.graphql
schemas.content:
type Query{
    #download pretreatment
    downloadProcess(bucketName:String,name:String,type:String):DownloadProcessData
}

#return data 
type DownloadProcessData{
    #error code
    code:Int
    #error message
    message:String
    #download request method
    method:String
    #download request url
    url:String
    #download request headers
    headers:DownloadHeaders
}

#download header type
type DownloadHeaders{
    #bucket name 
    bucketName:String
    #file name
    fileName:String
}
